{"tid":1909710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔咁得閒互屌，點解唔做...","createTime":"2020-03-04T07:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T08:20:12.000Z","uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce607918b364f7e9c3f37727ceb651f63ec7070","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:05:32.000Z","msg":"立會就9月先會有，重有一段時間<br />\n無論你係想選定杯葛<br />\n而家嘈來嘈去有咩意思，密密地做啦<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做實事啦</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n依家支共就搞到全球攬炒<br />\n<br />\n日本，韓國，意大利都大爆緊<br />\n歐洲都不遠了<br />\n<br />\n日落都唔會走得甩<br />\n<br />\n正所謂有危就有機，大家記唔記得隻支那肺炎係點來，幾時來，點解會爆發，支共做緊咩文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我幫大家回顧下2019年11月<br />\n支那肺炎 11月發現，9個人爆料被支共控罪 謠言罪<br />\n<br />\n到12月重唔比武漢上口罩防爆發<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果1月頭就開始大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家搞到全球都係<br />\n<br />\n但你有無發現無咩國際新聞講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支共獨裁使全球陷入危機</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n支共依家都未搞惦，想強迫復工都唔止，重係到打飛機，話教精人地國家<br />\n<br />\n而旗下kol就不斷散佈支肺係美國散佈出來想害支國的生化武器<br />\n<br />\n佢目標好明顯，就係想支肺變成全球問題同模糊自己先係起始之源，之後再外宣中共制度的優越性。<br />\n<br />\n等大家爆到咁下上就唔撚記得佐起源係點來，個個掛住保命。<br />\n<br />\n到最後只會做成該國政壇的變天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我地就係要趁依斷時間打斷佢外宣，用香港名義提醒全球支共先係一開始的罪人。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不斷就依件事講出獨裁政府會令全球陷入危機，再引出香港人要求民主係有其正當性同合理性。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果可以做到全球登報規模，將會對疫後抗爭打支好大的強心針。</span></div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b67c1c42c38d645dba79c0dd6f767d6f31aaea4","tid":1909710,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:07:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2795cc036f97fa8858624274a462f136c7722a76","tid":1909710,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"07d03a5f8282b1e707a381f3ce40c339f6657ce8","tid":1909710,"uid":303450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157cfb01f26ded5d845a51ab9eaa9b57f242b265","tid":1909710,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bca97a447079d99e1115c9313609bbc9e00772dc","tid":1909710,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5965fccd601bb0b822efe243c8eef026801dc685","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6c935a63fc306c78d99d0bad43dc0b9ab57c04","tid":1909710,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"和你捐"},{"pid":"c13d1611a67dab0bd624a90671abd5b844dc3fb9","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02da37e70c87ad45120cdabb281a5c5b13399faa","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91330ebbbea2416ec6396aa44f81ebe98ca7a288","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85786bbe97b300f581acb01e62a2544be988d05","tid":1909710,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2d3956438b98afe4d5a394ad3f484ce65dbf0a","tid":1909710,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"唔，咪比五毛分化<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dee282f907bea0998aa467e59dd91b01cccdf7a2","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62897df6eea397c4375f8c2421d7c670450807d5","tid":1909710,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ea0d718f79f122ab210d939d54ed7e3e84107f","tid":1909710,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"支持此項國際文宣"},{"pid":"47bd8b3eb060a0a6e09f3c99c5914821f95df4a4","tid":1909710,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid